OL,3,CWales' new rural affairs minister says
OL,4,Che is listening to farmers who
OL,5,Cprotested
OL,7,FThe Welsh Government's new cabinet
OL,8,Fsecretary for climate change and rural
OL,9,Faffairs, Huw Irranca-Davies MS, has
OL,10,Fpledged to listen to farmers after
OL,11,Fmonths of unrest.
OL,13,FIn his first interview since taking on
OL,14,Fthe role, Mr Irranca-Davies told ITV
OL,15,FCymru Wales that he realises concerns
OL,16,Ffrom the agricultural industry, but
OL,17,Fscrapping the sustainable farmers
OL,18,Fscheme (SFS) would be "the worst thing
OL,19,Fto do".
