OL,3,CWales' new rural affairs minister says
OL,4,Che is listening to farmers who
OL,5,Cprotested
OL,7,FThe new scheme is designed to make the
OL,8,Findustry greener by requiring farmers
OL,9,Fto plant 10% of their land with trees
OL,10,Fand use another 10% as wildlife
OL,11,Fhabitat to qualify for subsidies.
OL,13,FHowever, many farmers are strongly
OL,14,Fopposed to the policy, arguing it
OL,15,Fcould result in lower food production
OL,16,Flevels and job losses.
OL,18,FFarmers' unhappiness with the plans
OL,19,Fculminated in a protest outside the
OL,20,FSenedd where more than 3,000 turned up
OL,21,Fto make sure their voices were heard.
