OL,3,CWales' new rural affairs minister says
OL,4,Che is listening to farmers who
OL,5,Cprotested
OL,7,FSince then, First Minister Vaughan
OL,8,FGething has taken over from Mark
OL,9,FDrakeford, with a new rural affairs
OL,10,Fminister now in place.
OL,12,FMr Irranca-Davies said: "Farmers need
OL,13,Fto run businesses, but they also know
OL,14,Fthe key role that they have to do in
OL,15,Fplaying our part in responding to
OL,16,Fincreasingly traumatic weather and
OL,17,Fclimate change impacts."
