OL,3,CWales' new rural affairs minister says
OL,4,Che is listening to farmers who
OL,5,Cprotested
OL,7,FIt comes as a Freedom of Information
OL,8,Frequest by ITV Wales found more than
OL,9,F#50,000 was spent on policing the
OL,10,Fprotest against the Welsh Government's
OL,11,Fcontroversial policy.
OL,13,FLivestock farmer Liam Price organised
OL,14,Fthe protest. He said he wanted to see
OL,15,Fthe new cabinet secretary make it a
OL,16,Fpriority to look at the SFS.
OL,18,F"The biggest thing is he needs to look
OL,19,Fat every individual farm," said Liam.
OL,20,F"Some farms can do 10% (tree cover),
OL,21,Fsome farms can't."
