OL,3,CWales' new rural affairs minister says
OL,4,Che is listening to farmers who
OL,5,Cprotested
OL,7,FBut Mr Irranca-Davies said further
OL,8,Fupheaval would be the worst outcome,
OL,9,Fadmitting that while there were
OL,10,F"knotty areas" in the proposals, the
OL,11,Fworst thing for farmers would be to
OL,12,F"throw it up in the air and start
OL,13,Fagain".
OL,15,F"That gives them additional
OL,16,Funcertainty, on top of the additional
OL,17,Funcertainty that has been caused by
OL,18,Fthe withdrawal from the EU," he said,
OL,19,Fbefore adding that the Welsh
OL,20,FGovernment had noted concerns from the
OL,21,Fsector.
