OL,7,F"Farmers don't easily leave their land
OL,8,Fand drive up Cardiff to stand on the
OL,9,Fsteps of the Senedd and speak with
OL,10,FSenedd members in the numbers that
OL,11,Fthere were.
OL,13,F"They came from all parts of Wales -
OL,14,Fall types of farming as well. They
OL,15,Fwant us to listen and we are
OL,16,Flistening, we genuinely are."
